nd not on the basis of principles, ideas or philosophy, Sharma hoped that the leaders would come together again to reunite the party.","title":"HoR dissolution unfortunate: NCP leader Sharma - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/01/153450/","video":[]}
